      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six powerplant, renowned for its individual throttle bodies and high-revving double-VANOS architecture. This example is equipped with the desirable Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission and a factory-spec limited-slip differential. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including subframe reinforcement and a rod bearing service to ensure long-term structural and reciprocating assembly integrity. The chassis remains taut with refreshed bushings and dampers, preserving the communicative steering rack and balanced weight distribution. While the exterior shows light patina typical of a driven enthusiast car, the powertrain exhibits excellent compression and smooth power delivery throughout the rev range. A robust, driver-spec machine for the purist.",
